high_descs: Turn around and approach a coffeetable.
Pick up a knife from the coffeetable.
Align yourself with the table so that you are in front of a tomato.
Cut a tomato on the coffeetable using the knife.
Turn right, walk up to another coffeetable and look at it.
Cut a tomato on the table with the knife
Go back to the first coffeetable and face it from the left corner.
Put the knife on the coffeetable
Take a step right to the side to be right in front of the coffeetable.
Pick up a tomato slice from the coffeetable.
Turn around and walk across the room all the way to the opposite side and to a microwave.
Put the tomato slice in the microwave.
Turn around and all to the second coffeetable on the other side of the room.
Pick up a tomato slice from the coffeetable.
Turn around and walk back to the microwave.
Put the tomato slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around to the small coffee table directly ahead.
Pick up the butter knife from the table.
Look down at the tomato on the table.
Slice the tomato with the knife.
Turn right and go to the second small table ahead and to the left.
Slice the tomato on that table.
Turn left and go ahead to the first table.
Place the knife down on the table.
Look down at the tomato.
Pick up one slice of the tomato.
Turn around from the tomato and walk straight to the microwave at the far opposite end of the room.
Place the tomato slice into the microwave.
Return to the table where you sliced the second tomato.
Pick up another slice of tomato from this table.
Go back to the microwave.
Place the tomato slice into the microwave.
